    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Slack Bot Setup Instructions\n\n1. **Create Slack App:**\n   - Go to api.slack.com/apps\n   - Click 'Create New App'\n   - Choose 'From scratch'\n   - Name it 'WordPress Dev Assistant'\n   - Select your workspace\n\n2. **Configure Bot Permissions:**\n   - Navigate to OAuth & Permissions\n   - Add these Bot Token Scopes:\n     • app_mentions:read\n     • chat:write\n     • channels:history\n     • groups:history\n     • im:history\n     • mpim:history\n\n3. **Enable Event Subscriptions:**\n   - Go to Event Subscriptions\n   - Toggle ON\n   - Add webhook URL from n8n\n   - Subscribe to bot events:\n     • message.channels\n     • message.groups\n     • message.im\n     • app_mention\n\n4. **Install App to Workspace:**\n   - Go to Install App\n   - Click 'Install to Workspace'\n   - Copy Bot User OAuth Token\n   - Add to n8n credentials",
        "height": 520,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 3
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        60,
        140
      ],
      "id": "sticky-setup-1",
      "name": "Slack Setup Guide"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "string": [
